message:
Specialized training for investigating and prosecuting human trafficking crimes can help build cases that will keep perpetrators off the streets. When offenders are set free, individuals are at a greater risk of being victimized. 
#education #police #prosecutors #makingadifference #endhumantrafficking #pimplife to #lifeinjail
